title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 15 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 15 2022
description:
Joe Manchin sinks the Biden agenda again. Clay says, "If there was any sanity at all in the Democrat Party, they would be talking about nominating Joe Manchin to be their presidential candidate in 2024." Biden fist bumps MBS, uses covid as excuse. With Biden away, Gavin Newsom takes over the White House. The View accuses DeSantis of defrauding donors. Clay loved Buck's book recommendation, "Endurance." Sea lions attack beachgoers. Newsom goes after DeSantis.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
